      "description": "Clean, well-kept vehicle in good overall condition and a strong choice for someone who wants a solid, dependable driver without paying for a mint-condition example. It presents well inside and out, with normal age-appropriate wear but no major red flags in how it shows. The body and paint look good overall, the interior has been cared for, and it has the kind of condition most buyers hope to find in a properly maintained used car. Expect a nice-driving, honest vehicle that has been used but still shows well and should make a very satisfying daily driver.",
