      "description": "Value-priced and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle is a practical option for a budget-conscious buyer looking for affordable transportation. It shows its age and is best suited for someone who appreciates a straightforward, no-frills car with room to personalize or improve over time. An appealing choice for commuters, first-time buyers, or anyone seeking inexpensive mobility at a sensible price.",
