      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left in it? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who needs basic transportation, a first car, or a project to tinker with. It has the honest wear you\u2019d expect from an older vehicle, but it still has that dependable charm and could be a great fit for the right buyer. If you want something inexpensive and straightforward, this one is worth a look.",
